{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be clean and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Designs</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #e53935; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #f06292; /* Lighter Pink */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #ffffff;\n            --nav-text-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1100px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 0 20px;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--nav-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header .container {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            display: flex;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            margin-left: 20px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--nav-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, var(--secondary-color) 100%);\n            color: var(--nav-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .services {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .services h3 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-items {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n\n        .service-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .service-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--nav-text-color);\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .contact h3 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .contact p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .contact a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .contact a:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        /* Optional: Add Font Awesome for icons if needed */\n        @import url('https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css');\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Apex Designs</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <ul>\n                    <li><a href=\"#services\">Services</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#about\">About</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Transforming Ideas into Stunning Visuals</h2>\n            <p>We are a freelance design agency dedicated to crafting unique and impactful digital experiences.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\" class=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Services</h3>\n            <div class=\"service-items\">\n                <div class=\"service-item\">\n           